	.string "Black Knights are better than White\n"
	.string "Knights?$"

BLACK_KNIGHT_QUIZ_1_Text_4:
	.string "That is Faladorian talk.\p"
	.string "Prepare for battle scum!$"

BLACK_KNIGHT_QUIZ_1_Text_5:
	.string "â€¦$"

